items.name: Cable & Deadpool Vol. 2: The Burnt Offering (2007)
Cable & Deadpool Vol. 2: The Burnt Offering (Trade Paperback)

results.title: Dead Man's Switch Part One
results.description: Sandi discovers an amnesiac Alex Hayden and trains him, with the help of Outlaw and Taskmaster, to be a mercenary.

results.title: Dead Man's Switch Part Two
results.description: Alex & Outlaw are hired to steal the Punisher's guns

results.title: Dead Man's Switch Part Three
results.description: Alex and Outlaw battle some jewelry thieves.  Taskmaster leaves Sandi.  Mary Zero is introduced

results.title: Dead Man's Switch Part Four
results.description: Alex is shot and his theme park is burned.  Taskmaster sees Higashi asking Sandi out.

results.title: Dead Man's Switch Part Five
results.description: Arcade saves Alex's life, and offers to help rebuild his theme park.  Alex spends the issue unable to speak.

results.title: Dead Man's Switch Part Six
results.description: Alex, Outlaw and Taskmaster fight through an army of mercenaries.  Alex takes on Higashi as a client.
